    <note>Qiao(2) Ding [24399] He studied the Yi Jing in Sichuan and once visited Luoyang and met Cheng(1) Yi. Nobody knows where and when he died, but he was thought to have become an immortal (xianren). Important in the role played by the Yi Jing in linking Neo-Confucianism with Taoism. CBD, 5, 4263].</note>
